{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_11_03",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "coast-00-000-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ミニライブ前日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1166.6667025,
          "startTime": 1.1666667025
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 34633.3332062,
          "startTime": 34.6333332062
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 68899.99987289999,
          "startTime": 68.8999998729
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ、綺麗……この時間の海ってキラキラ光ってて\nいつ見ても綺麗だね、お姉ちゃん",
      "startTime": 8.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……でも、急に海が見たいだなんてどうしたの？\n明日はライブ本番だし、早めに帰らないと",
      "startTime": 17.7836223841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "うん。こっちに泊まるって言ってあるし\nお父さんとお母さんも待ってるよね",
      "startTime": 24.7666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "でもね、少しだけ……お姉ちゃんとお話がしたいんだ",
      "startTime": 27.9250786503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私と……？　曲も無事に完成したのに\nそんなに改まって、なんの話……？",
      "startTime": 38.1666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、実は、お姉ちゃんのノートを見ちゃったんだ\n私のために沢山悩んでくれてたんだね",
      "startTime": 47.1422217322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "っ、それは……",
      "startTime": 51.7241482774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "心配してくれてありがとう。でも、まだまだ頼りない\nかもだけど……私は大丈夫だから。安心して？",
      "startTime": 60.3079252094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "それを……今から見せてあげるね",
      "startTime": 65.8395445544,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4527.122112299992,
          "startTime": 70.3666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8793.7886518,
          "startTime": 74.6333332062
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗……？　靴なんて脱いで、どうしたの？\nま、待ちなさい、そっちは海……",
      "startTime": 74.3999998729,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4725.577072100009,
          "startTime": 79.125576945
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "coast-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 78.8589097697
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "けほ、けほ……お姉……ちゃん……？",
      "startTime": 79.925576945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗！　ごめんなさい……ごめんなさい……！\n私が目を離したせいで……！",
      "startTime": 89.9333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "もう二度と目を離したりしないから……！\n私が絶対に千紗を守るから……！",
      "startTime": 97.5999998729,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5122.108240700001,
          "startTime": 102.7221081136
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 39333.33333329999,
          "startTime": 136.9333332062
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 73833.33333329999,
          "startTime": 171.4333332062
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 108499.99491359999,
          "startTime": 206.0999947865
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 143999.9949136,
          "startTime": 241.5999947865
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "coast-00-000-evening",
      "startTime": 102.488773763
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗！　ダメ！　海に入っちゃ――",
      "startTime": 103.5221081136,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3603.1064828000012,
          "startTime": 107.1252145964
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4211.225092600003,
          "startTime": 107.7333332062
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "っ……ふぅ……大丈夫だよ、お姉ちゃん\nほら……私、平気だから……",
      "startTime": 113.6333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "無人島ロケの時に、雫ちゃんが海に入る練習に\n付き合ってくれたんだ",
      "startTime": 122.6999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "最初は怖かったけど、ちょっとずつ頑張って\n膝下くらいまでは入れるようになったの",
      "startTime": 129.2333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんや、みんなや……ファンの人達が\n私を支えてくれたおかげだよ？",
      "startTime": 137.9333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "だから、ゆっくりだったけど、私はここまでこれたし\n今もこうして前に進めてる。だから……『大丈夫』",
      "startTime": 147.0999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、そうよね。あの番組でも千紗は頑張って……\nゆっくりでも……その姿を、多くの人に見守られながら",
      "startTime": 162.9999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、千紗。私、千紗のことになるとすぐに\n不安や過保護になったりするところがあるのよね……",
      "startTime": 175.0999998729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "多分これは……子供の頃からそうだったから\nすぐには直せないかもしれない……",
      "startTime": 182.9333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "でも……ゆっくりでも、前に進んでいくわ\n千紗が見せてくれたみたいに",
      "startTime": 191.4333281199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ。良かった……安心してもらえたかな？\n……くしゅんっ！　す、少し冷えちゃったかも",
      "startTime": 199.8007438052,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5732.584314700006,
          "startTime": 205.5333281199
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6299.2509812999915,
          "startTime": 206.0999947865
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7299.2509812999915,
          "startTime": 207.0999947865
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7365.917647999993,
          "startTime": 207.1666614532
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "そっちに戻るね\n……わぁっ！？",
      "startTime": 207.0999947865,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1628.9570211000068,
          "startTime": 208.7289518076
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1628.9570211000068,
          "startTime": 208.7289518076
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4600.000000000023,
          "startTime": 211.6999947865
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.666666699995,
          "startTime": 211.7666614532
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.666666699995,
          "startTime": 211.7666614532
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2933.3385468000015,
          "startTime": 210.0333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4666.666666699995,
          "startTime": 211.7666614532
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "千紗！　私の手に掴まって……きゃっ！？\nいたたたた……千紗、大丈夫？　怪我はない？",
      "startTime": 213.0999947865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "うん。私は大丈夫\nでも、二人ともびしょ濡れになっちゃったね",
      "startTime": 224.4666614532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。……ふふ、ふふふ。あははは。服も髪も全部\n濡れちゃってるわね。帰ったらお風呂に入らないと",
      "startTime": 235.8612946122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
