      "text": "二曲続けてお楽しみ下さい！",
      "startTime": 329.0843542372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃんと、こうして肩を並べて）\n（ステージに立てることが、何よりも嬉しい）",
      "startTime": 337.700053787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
