      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "（今の嬉しさを、ここに来るまでの頑張りを）\n（そして、みんなへの感謝の気持ちを一杯込めて……）",
      "startTime": 347.2666960396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "（この曲で、私の姿で、沢山伝えたい……！）",
      "startTime": 352.2172806852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski021.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗、本当に素敵なアイドルになったわね）\n（でも……私だって負けないわ）",
      "startTime": 364.666665522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_11_03-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "（これまで育ててきた想いが、私のこれまでの歩みが）\n（聴いてくれる人達に届くように。全力で輝くわ……！）",
      "startTime": 373.5333138781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
